item.title: Blant Plog : 1_20200727
item.description: FOOD is GOOD. I love to eat things! Burgers, milkshakes, burritos, sushi, curry, potatoes, and that’s before noon. My friends and family wouldn’t tell me that I was a tubby 13 year-old directly, but I felt pretty thiccq. Alas! I was not alone. Between 2000 and 2018, 11.9% more of the entire American population became obese, while 4.5% more of it became severely obese. As long as the stuff gets onto our plates, why worry about the journey?
